   <p style="color: orangered;background-color: black;">Anirudh Ravichander (born 16 October 1990), also credited mononymously as Anirudh, is an Indian music composer, 
    and singer who works primarily in Tamil Cinema. He has also composed music for few Hindi and Telugu films. He has won two Filmfare Awards South,
     nine SIIMA Awards, six Edison Awards and five Vijay Awards.[2]
    </p>
